   <title class="- topic/title ">Auditing Considerations</title>
   <body class="- topic/body ">
      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Update 7-1 <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Auditing</i>: Auditing Accounting
                    Estimates, Including Fair Value Accounting Estimates, and Related
                    Disclosures</b>
         </p>
         <p outputclass="box" class="- topic/p ">In July 2020, the AICPA issued <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../../ps/ad_us_auditing_standards_aicpa_clarified/ad_section_500_599/ad_540/ad_540.dita#UUID-5e295753-fd8e-ad8d-74c0-3d4d49ef0274">Statement on Auditing Standards (SAS) No. 143</xref>, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Auditing Accounting Estimates and Related
                        Disclosures</i>, <ph class="- topic/ph ">
               <fn callout="6" id="UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6-aag-afi7-fn6" class="- topic/fn ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">All AU-C sections can be found in AICPA <xref format="dita" class="- topic/xref " href="../../../ps.dita#UUID-31e5d376-7dc9-0bde-c2d8-e38aa3d16588">
                        <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Professional
                                Standards</i>
                     </xref>. <unknown id="UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_N6617550070f09" class="- topic/unknown ">AICPA Professional Standards</unknown>
                  </p>
               </fn>
               <xref type="fn" class="- topic/xref " href="aag-afi7_auditing_considerations.dita#UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_UUID-b9c3ba0c-4485-4dc6-57e5-82cd3988dfc8/UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6-aag-afi7-fn6"/>
            </ph> which supersedes AU-C section 540, <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Auditing
                        Accounting Estimates, Including Fair Value Accounting Estimates, and Related
                        Disclosures</i> and amends the following AU-C sections: <unknown id="UUID-9a1b63a3-6faf-2f41-2eaf-f88a20adbbe6_N661755006fa93" class="- topic/unknown ">AU-C Section 540</unknown>
         </p>
